    "description": "Succeed co.,ltd. provides education and human resource services in Japan. The company operates through Educational Human Resources Support Business; Welfare Human Resources Support Business; Individualized Instruction Classroom Business; and Private Tutoring Business. It introduces and dispatches personnel to cram schools, educational corporations, etc.; and personnel to nursery schools, kindergartens, after-school care facilities, nursing homes, etc. The company also operates Individual Tutoring Academy Succeed and Pentas Kids; and provides private tutoring services to individuals. In addition, the company offers education-related services, including online services, such as private tutoring, running individualized cram schools, and human resource development for companies. Further, it provides human resources-related services comprising introducing, dispatching, and outsourcing personnel in the fields of education, childcare, and welfare, as well as undertakes the management of related services on a contract basis. Succeed co.,ltd. was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in Shinjuku, Japan."
